<text corresp="#EA" xml:lang="ta"><body>
   <milestone n="258" unit="page" facs="312"/>
   <p xml:id="KT400-kiḷavi"> <lb n="7"/>[itu, alar añci āṟṟāḷ ākiya talaimakaḷ talaivaṉ kēṭpāṉākat<lb n="8"/> tōḻikkuk kūṟiyatu.]
   <lb n="9"/>[tumpīmōci kīraṉ pāṭiyatu]</p>
   <lg xml:id="KT320">
   <l><lb n="10"/>320. peruṅkaṭaṟ paratavar koṇmī ṉuṇaṅkali</l>
   <l><lb n="11"/>ṉaruṅkaḻi koṇṭa viṟaviṉ vāṭaloṭu</l>
   <l><lb n="12"/>nilavuniṟa veṇmaṇal pullap palavuṭa</l>
   <l><lb n="13"/>ṉekkartoṟum parikkun tuṟaivaṉō ṭorunā</l>
   <l><lb n="14"/>ṇakkatōr paḻiyu milamē pōtaviḻ</l>
   <l><lb n="15"/>poṉṉiṇar marīiya puḷḷimiḻ poṅkarp</l>
   <l><lb n="16"/>puṉṉaiyañ cēri yivvūr</l>
   <l><lb n="17"/>koṉṉalar tūṟṟuṅ koṭumai yāṉē.</l></lg>

  <milestone n="306" unit="page" facs="358"/>
  <head><lb n="13"/>mullai.</head>
   <p xml:id="KT400-kilavi">
    <lb n="14"/>[itu, viṉaimuṟṟivanta talaimakaṉ tērppākaṉait talaiyaḷittatu.]
    <lb n="15"/>[pēyaṉār pāṭiyatu.]
  </p>
  <lg xml:id="KT400">
    <l><lb n="16"/>400. cēyāṟu cellā māyi ṉiṭariṉṟu</l>
    <l><lb n="17"/>kaṉaiik kāmam peruntōṭ keṉṟu</l>
    <l><lb n="18"/>naṉṟupurin teṇṇiya maṉattai yāki</l>
    <l><lb n="19"/>murampukaṇ ṇuṭaiya vēkik kaḷarik</l>
    <l><lb n="20"/>karampaip putuvaḻip paṭutta matiyuṭai</l>
    <l><lb n="21"/>valavō, yiṉṟu tantaṉai tērēr</l>
    <l><lb n="22"/>nōyuḻan tuṟaiviyai nalka lāṉē.</l>
  </lg>
  <p>
    <lb n="23"/>(i-ḷ.):― cēymaiyuḷḷa vaḻiyaik kaṭantu cellōmāṉāl, <lb n="24"/>periya tōḷkaḷaiyuṭaiyāḷukkuk kāmam mikuntu (ataṉāl,) tuṉ<lb n="25"/>pam (uṇṭākum) eṉṟu, peritum virumpi niṉaitta maṉattiṉai <lb n="26"/>yāy, murampiṭam· uṭaiyumpaṭi ceṉṟu kaḷarayuṭaiya pāḻnilaṅ<lb n="27"/>kaḷiṟ putuvaḻiyai uṇṭākkiya aṟivuḷḷa pāka ! iṉṟu tēraik <lb n="28"/>koṇarntaṉai ; (ataṉāl,) aḻakiya nōvāl varuntittaṅkumavaḷai <lb n="29"/>yāṉ talaiyaḷittalāṉ, (avaṭku iṭar) ilatāyiṟṟu. — (e - ṟu.)
  </p>
  <p>
    <pb n="307" facs="359"/>
    <lb n="1"/>murampu - kallirali uyarntirukkum nilam. karampai – pāḻ<lb n="2"/>nilam. viṉaiyāḷaṉai vēlaiyiṟutiyiṟ pukaḻtaṉ marapātaliṉ, ‘mati<lb n="3"/>yuṭai......tēr’ eṉṟuṉ. iṭar - mīṇṭuṅkoḷḷappaṭṭatu.
  </p>
  <p>
    <lb n="4"/>meyppāṭu ― perumitam. payaṉ ― pākaṉait talaiyaḷittal.
  </p>
</body></text></TEI>
